        <updateDate>2023-01-27T11:07:05Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Disaster and Emergency Pricing Abuse Prevention Act</b></p> <p>This bill makes it unlawful to sell, or offer for sale, an essential good or service at an unconscionably excessive price during, or in anticipation of, a natural disaster, pandemic, or state of emergency.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
